properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to Stonington, ME out 25 NM
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 16 at 6:45AM EST until February 16 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Caribou ME
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
seas 6 to 9 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to Stonington,
ME out 25 NM.

* WHEN...Until 1 PM EST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
